Integration with Java EE expression language.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttributeResolver
    Resolver for AbacSupport types.
    BuiltInMethods
    Built-in methods for expression language evaluation.
    JavaxElPolicyExecutor
    PolicyExecutor for Java EE Expression Language (EL).
    JavaxElPolicyExecutor.Builder
    A fluent API builder for JavaxElPolicyExecutor.
    JavaxElPolicyExecutorService
    Java service for JavaxElPolicyExecutor to be automatically added as a policy executor for ABAC.

Package io.helidon.security.abac.policy.el Description

Integration with Java EE expression language. Check BuiltInMethods to see all methods that are in default namespace and considered "built-in". Even these can be overridden by calling .Builder#addMethod(java.lang.String, java.lang.reflect.Method) with the same name.
